{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.95","c":"وَالْفَجْرِ","d":"wal-fajri","e":"demi fajar"}],"a":{"g":"By the dawn"}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"وَلَيَالٍ","d":"walayālin","e":"dan malam-malam"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.69","c":"عَشْرٍ","d":"ʿashrin","e":"sepuluh"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] ten nights"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.1","c":"وَالشَّفْعِ","d":"wal-shafʿi","e":"dan yang genap"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.79","c":"وَالْوَتْرِ","d":"wal-watri","e":"dan yang ganjil"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] the even [number] and the odd"}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.14","c":"وَاللَّيْلِ","d":"wa-al-layli","e":"dan malam"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.93","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"apabila"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.15","c":"يَسْرِ","d":"yasri","e":"berlalu"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] the night when it passes,"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.25","c":"هَلْ","d":"hal","e":"apakah/bukankah"},{"b":"0.4","h":"0.81","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"pada"},{"b":"0.9","h":"1.68","c":"ذَلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"itu/yang demikian"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.14","c":"قَسَمٌ","d":"qasamun","e":"sumpah"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.5","c":"لِذِي","d":"lidhī","e":"bagi memiliki"},{"b":"3.2","h":"5.79","c":"حِجْرٍ","d":"ḥij'rin","e":"akal"}],"a":{"g":"Is there [not] in [all] that an oath [sufficient] for one of perception?"}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"أَلَمْ","d":"alam","e":"tidakkah"},{"b":"0.54","h":"1.56","c":"تَرَ","d":"tara","e":"lihat/perhatikan"},{"b":"0.97","h":"2.34","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"kayfa","e":"bagaimana"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.5","c":"فَعَلَ","d":"faʿala","e":"berbuat"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.6","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"Tuhanmu"},{"b":"3.1","h":"6.25","c":"بِعَادٍ","d":"biʿādin","e":"terhadap kaum 'Ad"}],"a":{"g":"Have you not considered how your Lord dealt with 'Aad -","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                فتارة يتعرف إليهم في أفعاله المخوفة والمرجوة فيتلو عليهم سنته في أعدائه وفي أنبيائه فيقول: \"ألم تر كيف فعل ربك بعاد إرم ذات العماد - ألم تر كيف فعل ربك بأصحاب الفيل\".\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, at times He makes Himself known to them through His acts that inspire fear and hope, and He recites to them His established way [sunnah] with His enemies and with His prophets, saying: \"Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with 'Aad, Iram of the pillars [Iram dhat al-'imad]? Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with the companions of the elephant [ashab al-fil]?\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"إِرَمَ","d":"irama","e":"kaum Iram"},{"b":"0.55","h":"1.07","c":"ذَاتِ","d":"dhāti","e":"memiliki"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.39","c":"الْعِمَادِ","d":"l-ʿimādi","e":"tiang/bangunan tinggi"}],"a":{"g":"[With] Iram - who had lofty pillars,"}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"الَّتِي","d":"allatī","e":"yang"},{"b":"1.0","h":"2.24","c":"لَمْ","d":"lam","e":"tidak/belum"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.84","c":"يُخْلَقْ","d":"yukh'laq","e":"diciptakan/dibangun"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.35","c":"مِثْلُهَا","d":"mith'luhā","e":"seperti itu/serupa itu"},{"b":"3.3","h":"6.38","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"pada"},{"b":"3.6","h":"6.82","c":"الْبِلَادِ","d":"l-bilādi","e":"negeri"}],"a":{"g":"The likes of whom had never been created in the land?"}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.45","c":"وَثَمُودَ","d":"wathamūda","e":"dan Samud"},{"b":"1.0","h":"2.09","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"orang-orang yang"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.92","c":"جَابُوا","d":"jābū","e":"(mereka) memotong"},{"b":"2.8","h":"5.08","c":"الصَّخْرَ","d":"l-ṣakhra","e":"batu-batu besar"},{"b":"3.6","h":"6.73","c":"بِالْوَادِ","d":"bil-wādi","e":"di lembah"}],"a":{"g":"And [with] Thamud, who carved out the rocks in the valley?"}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"وَفِرْعَوْنَ","d":"wafir'ʿawna","e":"dan Fir'aun"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.14","c":"ذِي","d":"dhī","e":"memiliki"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.58","c":"الْأَوْتَادِ","d":"l-awtādi","e":"pasak-pasak (bala tentara)"}],"a":{"g":"And [with] Pharaoh, owner of the stakes? -"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"orang-orang yang"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.84","c":"طَغَوْا","d":"ṭaghaw","e":"(mereka) melampui batas"},{"b":"1.7","h":"4.05","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"pada"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.53","c":"الْبِلَادِ","d":"l-bilādi","e":"negeri-negeri itu"}],"a":{"g":"[All of] whom oppressed within the lands"}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.05","c":"فَأَكْثَرُوا","d":"fa-aktharū","e":"lalu mereka banyak berbuat"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.26","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fīhā","e":"didalamnya"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.54","c":"الْفَسَادَ","d":"l-fasāda","e":"kerusakan"}],"a":{"g":"And increased therein the corruption."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"فَصَبَّ","d":"faṣabba","e":"maka menimpakan"},{"b":"0.83","h":"1.27","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"atas mereka"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.15","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"Tuhanmu"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.75","c":"سَوْطَ","d":"sawṭa","e":"cemeti/cambuk"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.96","c":"عَذَابٍ","d":"ʿadhābin","e":"azab"}],"a":{"g":"So your Lord poured upon them a scourge of punishment."}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"sesungguhnya"},{"b":"1.2","h":"1.6","c":"رَبَّكَ","d":"rabbaka","e":"Tuhanmu"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.24","c":"لَبِالْمِرْصَادِ","d":"labil-mir'ṣādi","e":"benar-benar mengawasi"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, your Lord is in observation."}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"فَأَمَّا","d":"fa-ammā","e":"maka adapun"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.5","c":"الْإِنْسَانُ","d":"l-insānu","e":"manusia"},{"b":"3.5","h":"5.09","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"apabila"},{"b":"4.2","h":"6.18","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"apa"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.51","c":"ابْتَلَاهُ","d":"ib'talāhu","e":"mengujinya"},{"b":"5.5","h":"8.29","c":"رَبُّهُ","d":"rabbuhu","e":"Tuhannya"},{"b":"6.5","h":"10.13","c":"فَأَكْرَمَهُ","d":"fa-akramahu","e":"lalu Dia memuliakannya"},{"b":"8.0","h":"12.89","c":"وَنَعَّمَهُ","d":"wanaʿʿamahu","e":"dan Dia memberikan nikmat padanya"},{"b":"9.5","h":"15.33","c":"فَيَقُولُ","d":"fayaqūlu","e":"maka ia akan berkata"},{"b":"10.6","h":"17.21","c":"رَبِّي","d":"rabbī","e":"Tuhanku"},{"b":"13.2","h":"19.49","c":"أَكْرَمَنِ","d":"akramani","e":"Dia telah memuliakanku"}],"a":{"g":"And as for man, when his Lord tries him and [thus] is generous to him and favors him, he says, \"My Lord has honored me.\"","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                والمغرور إذا أقبلت عليه الدنيا ظن أنها كرامة من الله، وإذا صرفت عنه ظن أنها هوان، كما أخبر الله تعالى عنه إذ قال \"فأما الإنسان إذا ما ابتلاه ربه فأكرمه ونعمه فيقول ربي أكرمن وأما إذا ما ابتلاه فقدر عليه رزقه فيقول ربي أهانن\" فأجاب الله عن ذلك \"كلا\" أي ليس كما قال إنما هو ابتلاء نعوذ بالله من شر البلاء ونسأل الله التثبيت، فبين أن ذلك غرور. قال الحسن كذبهما جميعاً بقوله \"كلا\" يقول ليس هذا بإكرامي ولا هذا بهواني، ولكن الكريم من أكرمته بطاعتي غنياً كان أو فقيراً، والمهان من أهنته بمعصيتي غنياً كان أو فقيراً.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, the deluded one [al-maghruur], when the world [al-dunya] turns towards him, thinks it is an honor [karaamah] from God, and when it is turned away from him, thinks it is a humiliation [ihaanah], just as God, the Exalted, informed about him when He said: \"As for man, when his Lord tests him, honoring him and bestowing favor upon him, he says, 'My Lord has honored me.' But when He tests him and restricts his provision, he says, 'My Lord has humiliated me.'\" So God answered concerning that: \"No [kallaa]\" — meaning, it is not as he said; it is only a trial [ibtilaa']. We seek refuge in God from the evil of the trial, and we ask God for steadfastness. Thus, He made clear that this is delusion [ghuruur]. Al-Hasan said: He declared them both false with His saying \"No [kallaa],\" meaning: This is not My honoring, nor is this My humiliation. Rather, the honored one [al-kareem] is he whom I have honored through his obedience to Me, whether he be rich or poor, and the humiliated one [al-muhaan] is he whom I have humiliated through his disobedience to Me, whether he be rich or poor.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"وَأَمَّا","d":"wa-ammā","e":"dan adapun/tetapi"},{"b":"1.5","h":"4.13","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"apabila"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.19","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"apa"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.5","c":"ابْتَلَاهُ","d":"ib'talāhu","e":"mengujinya"},{"b":"4.9","h":"7.25","c":"فَقَدَرَ","d":"faqadara","e":"lalu Dia menentukan/menyempitkan"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.59","c":"عَلَيْهِ","d":"ʿalayhi","e":"atasnya"},{"b":"6.7","h":"10.07","c":"رِزْقَهُ","d":"riz'qahu","e":"rizkinya"},{"b":"7.7","h":"11.86","c":"فَيَقُولُ","d":"fayaqūlu","e":"lalu dia akan berkata"},{"b":"8.8","h":"13.76","c":"رَبِّي","d":"rabbī","e":"Tuhanku"},{"b":"11.0","h":"16.44","c":"أَهَانَنِ","d":"ahānani","e":"Dia menghinaku"}],"a":{"g":"But when He tries him and restricts his provision, he says, \"My Lord has humiliated me.\""}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"كَلَّا","d":"kallā","e":"sekali-kali tidak"},{"b":"1.2","h":"3.45","c":"بَلْ","d":"bal","e":"tetapi/bahkan"},{"b":"1.7","h":"4.24","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"tidak"},{"b":"2.0","h":"4.9","c":"تُكْرِمُونَ","d":"tuk'rimūna","e":"kamu memuliakan"},{"b":"3.3","h":"7.14","c":"الْيَتِيمَ","d":"l-yatīma","e":"anak yatim"}],"a":{"g":"No! But you do not honor the orphan"}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.04","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"dan tidak"},{"b":"0.6","h":"0.94","c":"تَحَاضُّونَ","d":"taḥāḍḍūna","e":"saling menganjurkan"},{"b":"4.2","h":"6.04","c":"عَلَى","d":"ʿalā","e":"atas"},{"b":"4.9","h":"7.34","c":"طَعَامِ","d":"ṭaʿāmi","e":"memberi makan"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.97","c":"الْمِسْكِينِ","d":"l-mis'kīni","e":"orang miskin"}],"a":{"g":"And you do not encourage one another to feed the poor."}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.76","c":"وَتَأْكُلُونَ","d":"watakulūna","e":"dan kamu memakan"},{"b":"1.4","h":"3.13","c":"التُّرَاثَ","d":"l-turātha","e":"harta warisan"},{"b":"2.4","h":"5","c":"أَكْلًا","d":"aklan","e":"dengan makan"},{"b":"2.8","h":"6.16","c":"لَمًّا","d":"lamman","e":"loba"}],"a":{"g":"And you consume inheritance, devouring [it] altogether,"}},"20":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.05","c":"وَتُحِبُّونَ","d":"watuḥibbūna","e":"dan kamu mencintai"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.46","c":"الْمَالَ","d":"l-māla","e":"harta"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.92","c":"حُبًّا","d":"ḥubban","e":"cinta"},{"b":"2.9","h":"6","c":"جَمًّا","d":"jamman","e":"berlebihan"}],"a":{"g":"And you love wealth with immense love."}},"21":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"كَلَّا","d":"kallā","e":"sekali-kali tidak"},{"b":"1.4","h":"3.19","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"apabila"},{"b":"1.9","h":"4.37","c":"دُكَّتِ","d":"dukkati","e":"digoncangkan/dihancurkan"},{"b":"2.8","h":"5.87","c":"الْأَرْضُ","d":"l-arḍu","e":"bumi"},{"b":"3.6","h":"7.36","c":"دَكًّا","d":"dakkan","e":"goncangan"},{"b":"5.3","h":"9.58","c":"دَكًّا","d":"dakkan","e":"goncangan"}],"a":{"g":"No! When the earth has been leveled - pounded and crushed -"}},"22":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.29","c":"وَجَاءَ","d":"wajāa","e":"dan datang"},{"b":"2.2","h":"2.47","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"Tuhanmu"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.16","c":"وَالْمَلَكُ","d":"wal-malaku","e":"dan malaikat"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.92","c":"صَفًّا","d":"ṣaffan","e":"berbaris"},{"b":"5.8","h":"7.27","c":"صَفًّا","d":"ṣaffan","e":"baris"}],"a":{"g":"And your Lord has come and the angels, rank upon rank,"}},"23":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"وَجِاىءَ","d":"wajīa","e":"dan didatangkan/diperlihatkan"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.41","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"yawma-idhin","e":"pada hari itu"},{"b":"4.4","h":"6.03","c":"بِجَهَنَّمَ","d":"bijahannama","e":"neraka Jahanam"},{"b":"7.3","h":"10.4","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"yawma-idhin","e":"pada hari itu"},{"b":"9.3","h":"12.96","c":"يَتَذَكَّرُ","d":"yatadhakkaru","e":"akan ingat"},{"b":"10.5","h":"15.2","c":"الْإِنْسَانُ","d":"l-insānu","e":"manusia"},{"b":"12.6","h":"18.11","c":"وَأَنَّى","d":"wa-annā","e":"dan bagaimana"},{"b":"14.4","h":"20.47","c":"لَهُ","d":"lahu","e":"baginya"},{"b":"14.8","h":"21.53","c":"الذِّكْرَى","d":"l-dhik'rā","e":"ingat/mengingat"}],"a":{"g":"And brought [within view], that Day, is Hell - that Day, man will remember, but what good to him will be the remembrance?"}},"24":{"w":[{"b":"0.06","h":"0.07","c":"يَقُولُ","d":"yaqūlu","e":"dia berkata"},{"b":"0.91","h":"2.1","c":"يَالَيْتَنِي","d":"yālaytanī","e":"alangkah baiknya aku dulu"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.23","c":"قَدَّمْتُ","d":"qaddamtu","e":"aku dahulukan/kerjakan"},{"b":"3.4","h":"6.25","c":"لِحَيَاتِي","d":"liḥayātī","e":"untuk hidupku"}],"a":{"g":"He will say, \"Oh, I wish I had sent ahead [some good] for my life.\""}},"25":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"فَيَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"fayawma-idhin","e":"maka pada hari itu"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.76","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"tidak"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.88","c":"يُعَذِّبُ","d":"yuʿadhibu","e":"menyiksa"},{"b":"2.9","h":"5.61","c":"عَذَابَهُ","d":"ʿadhābahu","e":"siksa-Nya"},{"b":"5.8","h":"9.07","c":"أَحَدٌ","d":"aḥadun","e":"seorang/satu"}],"a":{"g":"So on that Day, none will punish [as severely] as His punishment,"}},"26":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"dan tidak"},{"b":"0.6","h":"1.47","c":"يُوثِقُ","d":"yūthiqu","e":"mengikat"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.09","c":"وَثَاقَهُ","d":"wathāqahu","e":"ikatan-Nya"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.4","c":"أَحَدٌ","d":"aḥadun","e":"seorang/satu"}],"a":{"g":"And none will bind [as severely] as His binding [of the evildoers]."}},"27":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.55","c":"يَاأَيَّتُهَا","d":"yāayyatuhā","e":"hai"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.21","c":"النَّفْسُ","d":"l-nafsu","e":"jiwa/diri"},{"b":"4.7","h":"6.13","c":"الْمُطْمَئِنَّةُ","d":"l-muṭ'ma-inatu","e":"tenang"}],"a":{"g":"[To the righteous it will be said], \"O reassured soul,","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وأما فعله فقد ذكر في قوله تعالى: ﴿ ياأيها النفس المطمئنة ارجعى إلى ربك راضية مرضية فادخلى في عبادى وادخلى جنتى ﴾ {} ولنرجع الآن إلى الغرض فإن المقصود ذكر نعم الله تعالى في الأكل فقد ذكرنا بعض نعم الله تعالى في آلات الأكل.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                And as for His action, it has been mentioned in His saying, the Most High: \"O soul [nafs] at peace [mutma'innah], return to your Lord, well-pleased and well-pleasing. So enter among My servants, and enter My Paradise [jannah].\" (89:27-30)\n\nAnd let us now return to the purpose, for the intended aim is to mention the blessings [ni'am] of Allah, the Most High, in eating. We have already mentioned some of the blessings of Allah, the Most High, in the instruments of eating.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"28":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"ارْجِعِي","d":"ir'jiʿī","e":"kembalilah"},{"b":"2.3","h":"2.79","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"kepada"},{"b":"3.0","h":"3.83","c":"رَبِّكِ","d":"rabbiki","e":"Tuhanmu"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.48","c":"رَاضِيَةً","d":"rāḍiyatan","e":"rida/puas"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.59","c":"مَرْضِيَّةً","d":"marḍiyyatan","e":"diridhoi"}],"a":{"g":"Return to your Lord, well-pleased and pleasing [to Him],"}},"29":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"فَادْخُلِي","d":"fa-ud'khulī","e":"maka masuklah"},{"b":"0.98","h":"1.72","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"dalam"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.44","c":"عِبَادِي","d":"ʿibādī","e":"hamba-Ku"}],"a":{"g":"And enter among My [righteous] servants"}},"30":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"وَادْخُلِي","d":"wa-ud'khulī","e":"dan masuklah"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.99","c":"جَنَّتِي","d":"jannatī","e":"surga-Ku"}],"a":{"g":"And enter My Paradise.\""}}}